Juliet Kabera ni Umuyobozi mukuru w'ikigo gishinzwe gucunga ibidukikije mu Rwanda.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/rwanda-rallies-global-support-beat-plastic-pollution</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Juliet Kabera numuyobozi wikigo gishinzwe Kurinda Ibidukije Mu Rwanda (REMA ) , Akaba yarashyizweho muri Gicurasi 2020. Mbere yo gushyirwaho, yari afite umuyobozi mukuru w’ibidukikije n’imihindagurikire y’ibihe muri Minisiteri y’ibidukikije. Nyakanga . Juliet yabaye Umuyobozi wa Komite Nyobozi y'Ikigega Cyinshi cya Protokole ya Montreal mu mwaka wa 2019/2020.<ref>https://www.rema.gov.rw/index.php?id=48</ref>

== Amashuri Yize ==
Juliet KABERA yahawe impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor muri  Siyanse  yize ibijyanye na Biochemie yakuye muri kaminuza ya Makerere Kampala, muri Werurwe 2002, naho muri Kamena 2020 arangiza Masters muri Conservation MBA muri kaminuza Nyafurika y'Ubuyobozi.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/node/886973</ref>

== Icyo Avuga muguca Amashashi Mu Rwanda ==
Kabera yavuze ko uburambe bw’imyanda ya pulasitike bwagaragaje akamaro k’ubufatanye bw’igihugu, uturere ndetse n’amahanga mu rwego rwo kurwanya umwanda.Ati: "Nyuma y'ibiganiro bikomeye mu mezi ashize, twishimiye intambwe imaze guterwa mu rwego mpuzamahanga rwemewe n'amategeko ku bijyanye no kwanduza plastike".<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/rwanda-rallies-global-support-beat-plastic-pollution</ref>

Umushinga w’icyemezo uremera imiterere y’imipaka y’ikibazo cy’umwanda wa pulasitike kandi ko ari ngombwa kuwukemura aho uturuka.Yavuze ko hakenewe gushyirwaho amategeko akomeye na politiki haba ku rwego rw'igihugu ndetse no ku isi hose, agira ati: “Kubera ko umwanda wa plastike ari ikibazo cyambukiranya imipaka, dushobora kugikemura dukorera hamwe.”<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/rwanda-rallies-global-support-beat-plastic-pollution</ref>

